column2: cbind(colnames(df2_num_filtered), result) %>% as_tibble() %>% mutate(asv=colnames.df2_num_filtered.) %>% left_join(taxa) %>% left_join(HOMD_mapping) %>% filter(padj < 0.05) %>% select(-Kingdom,-Phylum,-Class,-Order,-Family,-representative_sequence,-colnames.df2_num_filtered.) %>% arrange(padj) %>% print(n=nrow(.))
